local Manager = s_WordDictionaryDatabase; Manager.allwords["isthmus"]={"isthmus","['ɪsθməs; 'ɪstməs; 'ɪsməs]","['ɪsməs]","n.地峡",'n.地峡，[解]峡，管峡','The north and south of the island are linked by a narrow isthmus.','岛的北部和南部由一条狭窄的地峡相连。','Yet John Underhill of Edinburgh University has found evidence that the isthmus is full of landslide rubble, which could have tumbled into a narrow sea channel during an earthquake.','然而，爱丁堡大学的约翰•安德希尔发现证据显示这个地峡布满了山崩后的砾石，它们可以在发生地震时滚落到一个狭窄的海峡里。'}
